---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title = "Contacto">

<div class = "contacto">
    <section class="relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto md:flex-row p-14 md:py-[60px] md:px-20" id="contact">
        <div class="row items-center py-5 md:w-5/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10">
            <div class="text-left space-y-3">
                <form class="ml-auo space-y-4">
                    <input type='text' placeholder='Nombre'
                        class="w-full rounded-md py-2.5 px-4 border-black border-2 placeholder:text-slate-400" />
                    <input type='email' placeholder='Email'
                        class="w-full rounded-md py-2.5 px-4 border-black border-2 placeholder:text-slate-400" />
                    <input type='text' placeholder='Asunto'
                        class="w-full rounded-md py-2.5 px-4 border-black border-2 placeholder:text-slate-400" />
                    <textarea placeholder='¿En que te puedo ayudar?' rows="6"
                        class="w-full rounded-md px-4 pt-2.5 border-black border-2 placeholder:text-slate-400"></textarea>
                    <div class="grid grid-rows-1 grid-flow-col gap-2">
                        <button type='button' class="boton text-white bg-black font-semibold rounded-md text-sm px-4 py-2.5 w-full">Enviar
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-6/12 md:pb-20 md:pt-10 md:pl-20">
            <div class="text-left space-y-3">
                <h2 class="font-poppins text-4xl font-bold sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl">
                    Hablemos de <span class="text-white font-sans font-outline-sm md:font-outline"> Ideas </span> que cobran vida <br> 

                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-white pt-3">
                Fusiono datos, desarrollo y creatividad para diseñar experiencias interactivas, intuitivas y memorables. Más que código, creo arte digital que conecta, impacta e inspira.
                </p>
                <p class="text-xl font-medium md:pt-8">
                    christianlara225@aragon.unam.mx <br>
                    5636538990
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<style>
    .contacto {
        background-color: #8844e4;
        color: #f0fc44;
    }
    .boton:hover {
        background-color: #f0fc44;
        color: #8844e4;
        transition: 0.5s;
        transform: 1.1s;
    }
</style>

</Layout>